      <title>墨西哥在打击贩毒行动中逮捕两名毒枭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/mexico-arrests-two-drug-lords-in-operation-against-trafficking</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥当局在加强锡那罗亚州安全行动中逮捕了两名毒枭，该州深陷贩毒集团各派系之间暴力冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/mexico-arrests-two-drug-lords-in-operation-against-trafficking</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 02:21:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>玻利维亚检察官对埃沃·莫拉莱斯发出逮捕令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bolivia-prosecutors-issue-arrest-warrant-for-evo-morales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玻利维亚检察官周一表示，因涉及一名 15 岁未成年人性虐待指控的调查，已对前总统埃沃莫拉莱斯发出了逮捕令。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/bolivia-prosecutors-issue-arrest-warrant-for-evo-morales</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:55:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普任命前投资银行家格拉斯为日本大使</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/trump-picks-former-investment-banker-glass-as-japan-ambassador</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布任命乔治·格拉斯为驻日本大使，在美国政府寻求加强对华立场之际，这一职位对于其盟友来说至关重要。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/trump-picks-former-investment-banker-glass-as-japan-ambassador</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:52:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国政府被指控允许污水泄漏违反法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-government-accused-of-breaking-law-by-allowing-sewage-spills</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家公共监督机构周二表示，英国政府和监管机构允许水务公司在没有下雨的情况下将未经处理的污水排入支流，违反了法律，并威胁要采取法律行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/uk-government-accused-of-breaking-law-by-allowing-sewage-spills</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>劳斯莱斯和英国保诚集团助力制定英国工业战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/rolls-royce-prudential-to-help-devise-uk-industrial-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默领导的英国政府正在制定新的产业战略以推动增长，来自劳斯莱斯控股有限公司、英国保诚集团和法国法律与通用集团等公司的高层将为其提供建议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/rolls-royce-prudential-to-help-devise-uk-industrial-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>曾流亡的泰国国王儿子称王室必须允许批评</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/once-exiled-son-of-thai-king-says-royals-must-allow-criticism</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当他抵达泰国北部的一所学校时，数百名村民立即起立，双手合十，以传统方式表示敬意。一些人甚至跪下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-17/once-exiled-son-of-thai-king-says-royals-must-allow-criticism</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Dec 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的豁免权主张未能终结纽约封口费案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-loses-bid-to-have-hush-money-case-tossed-over-immunity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普未能说服法官以总统豁免权为由撤销对其在纽约封口费案中的定罪，但由于这位当选总统继续对判决提出质疑，目前尚不清楚该案是否仍将进入宣判阶段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-loses-bid-to-have-hush-money-case-tossed-over-immunity</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 23:44:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芝加哥官员通过 2025 年预算，不上调房产税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/chicago-officials-approve-2025-budget-without-property-tax-hike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在芝加哥市长布兰登·约翰逊取消了其提出的房产税上调提议后，芝加哥市议会批准了 2025 年约 170 亿美元的预算，其中征税和费用将增加约 2.56 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/chicago-officials-approve-2025-budget-without-property-tax-hike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 23:15:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>罗伯特·肯尼迪 (RFK) 小儿子争取共和党人的支持，争取最高卫生职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/rfk-jr-courts-republicans-in-effort-to-secure-top-health-job</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小罗伯特·F·肯尼迪正在会见共和党参议员，他们希望更好地了解他对堕胎和疫苗政策的看法，他本周将争取共和党参议员支持他被提名出任卫生与公众服务部高级职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/rfk-jr-courts-republicans-in-effort-to-secure-top-health-job</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 20:29:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普谴责无人机“悬念” 白宫称无风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-us-military-keeping-public-in-suspense-on-drones</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此前，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普暗示美国政府让美国人对这些无人机目击事件“心存疑虑”，白宫表示，执法部门对新泽西州和其他东北部各州报告的数千起无人机目击事件进行了评估，认为没有必要感到恐慌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/trump-says-us-military-keeping-public-in-suspense-on-drones</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 17:30:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
